{"tid":480164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國留日學生涉嫌將美國軍用夜視鏡經香港運入中國","createTime":"2017-11-26T00:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T16:57:38.000Z","uid":144229,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b89cfe1d9d32cb5749861089c550f490ab2a17e","tid":480164,"uid":144229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:18:57.000Z","msg":"【美精密夜視技術或流入中國】<br />\n【華留日學生網上淘得經港運廣州】<br />\n<br />\n日本東京一個中國留學生，涉嫌將軍用夜視儀經香港出口到中國被捕。<br />\n<br />\n當局指有承包商虛報銷毀了該夜視儀，實際轉售及放上網拍賣，相信美國軍事技術經日本流入中國。<br />\n<br />\n有線電視報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/763352837190120/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F763352837190120%2F&d=3WmJyH6EkxGsGwayycMgSDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=70763a6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/763352837190120/</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得應該用間碟罪同走私軍火嘅罪名告佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a41332ebe442c528ed25bce47684c4a6ce42ea","tid":480164,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:24:15.000Z","msg":"賣比邪惡軸心國 <br />\n全世界人民公敵"},{"pid":"43a2f09e87311ff0b83e9018a04a0db15da8a5d3","tid":480164,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:41:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣比邪惡軸心國 <br />\n全世界人民公敵</blockquote><br />\n肯定有人指使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce2ef41da5b70bd674d4568cd77602b8a4b7631","tid":480164,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:04:34.000Z","msg":"支那口交部: 美國人自編自導自演"},{"pid":"d940c1dbb1c7c187a20e0e805bb0bdea96c40303","tid":480164,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:05:52.000Z","msg":"支那口交部: 事主於中國出生，但非中國籍"},{"pid":"352f3dc8d4418d1d1bc6cd2ce773c4186581fa9d","tid":480164,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor